        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2023-06-20 13:22:55.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nHi @Bhagyalakshmi, \nAccording to Waqas, it seems to be ok but before we merge you need to test a whole set of create NS, Instantiate NS, Terminate NS and Delete NS test cases. \n\nSo, it would be great if you do a local test for the CreateNS-InstantiateNS-TerminateNS-DeleteNS.\n\nOptionally, Waqas suggested to use the CSIT for this. \n\n- clone the csit project, https://gerrit.onap.org/r/admin/repos/integration/csit \n- modify the line 431 for your local image version, https://github.com/onap/integration-csit/blob/master/plans/so/integration-etsi-testing/docker-compose.yml#L431 \nfor example, \nfrom image: ${NEXUS_DOCKER_REPO_MSO}/onap/so/so-etsi-nfvo-ns-lcm:${ETSI_NFVO_NS_LCM_IMAGE_VERSION} to \nimage: onap/so/so-etsi-nfvo-ns-lcm:${ETSI_NFVO_NS_LCM_IMAGE_VERSION}\n- cd into the project and then run the following to run the integration tests, ./run-csit.sh plans/so/integration-etsi-testing/ \n\nPlease let me know your local test results.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
